fields.title: Test Bundle
fields.description: Testing the HTML parse times, style recalculations, paint times and layout placing times of different implementations of a same design. Great thanks to Solucija for offering their great design for projects like this.

fields.name: Solucija, bundle 1
fields.description: Original implementation of the page as found on http://www.solucija.com/template/distinctive.

fields.name: Solucija 2, bundle 1
fields.description: Implementation provided by a friend. Differs very little from the original.

fields.name: Solucija 3, bundle 1
fields.description: My own implementation, using tags that seemd appropriate for the layout and styling with a CSS reset.

fields.name: Solucija 5, bundle 1

fields.title: Quirks
fields.abstract: A list of known quirks I have to warn you about.
fields.content:
I don't want to scare anyone, but I have found the following quirks on my own and I have to warn you about them in advance.

  1. When you close the measurement tab, the main tab crashes - though it's annoying, there's nothing wrong with this. I have the suspect bugs for this on my kill list :)

At this moment there's only one problem I've found, but feel free to tell me about any oddity you encounter via the email found in the footer of the page.
